<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM9.7.5">
<l>mañcutōy veṇkuṭai maṉṉarāy vāraṇañ cūḻa vāḻntār</l>
<l>tuñciṉā reṉpatōr collainī tuyareṉak karuti ṉāyēl</l>
<l>nañcutōy koṅkaimē laṅkaivāy vaittavaḷ nāḷai yuṇṭa</l>
<l>mañcaṉār vallavāḻ collumā vallaiyāy maruvu neñcē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>If you think that the comment saying, “[Even] those who lived as kings,</l>
<l>While surrounded by defenses with white umbrellas that touch the clouds, died,” is sad,</l>
<l>Oh, heart, firmly embrace the way that tells of Vallavāḻ, [the city of] the boy</l>
<l rend="indent">who consumed [all of] her days,</l>
<l>Putting his lips and fine hands on the breast touched with poison.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
